## Commands

```bash
# Package management (PDM)
pdm install                          # Install dependencies

# Development
pdm run startdev 8000                # Run development server
pdm run makemigrations               # Create migrations
pdm run migrate                      # Apply migrations
pdm run createsu                     # Create superuser

# Testing
pdm run pytest                       # Run all tests

# Linting
pdm run lint-check                   # Run black --check + pylint

# Celery (local development)
celery -A main worker -l info
celery -A main beat -l info

# Static files
pdm run collectstatic
```

